  "texts": [
    "(13) depicts the number of cells as well as the composition of the execution times for varying Mapprox.",
    "Although the number of cells increases with an improved approximation of the metric, reduction rates of 65% for the tandem configuration and 76% for the cylinder are achievable even with Mapprox = 1.",
    "It should be noted that the choice of the metric significantly influences the overall mesh reduction and must be done carefully.",
    "The total execution time (ttot) is composed of the uniform refinement (tuni), metric-based refinement (ta), geometry refinement (tg), and the final mesh renumbering (trn).",
    "(13), it can be seen that adaptive refinement significantly dominates the overall execution time for larger mesh sizes."
